						<summary>

						<p>Records the gift of 12 <hi rend="italic">Bhujabala-māḍai</hi> for a brass lamp with tripod stand in the temple by <hi rend="bold">Nūṅkama-Mahādēvi,</hi> wife of <hi rend="bold">Madhurāntakap-Pottappichchōḻan</hi> <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> <hi rend="bold">Siddharaśaṉ.</hi> The inscription is dated in the <hi rend="bold">19th year</hi> of the king's reign.</p>						

						</summary>
